Name: PROCESSOR INTEGRATION TIME SINCE DETECTION IN MINUTES
Explanation: TIME BETWEEN SIGNAL RECEPTION AND DISPLAY.

Name: TIME IN STATE IN MINUTES
Explanation: TIME OF EACH EPISODE OF AN ASW MISSION.

Name: TIME REQUIRED TO BRING UNIT TO FLYING STATIONS IN MIN
Explanation: THE TIME IN MINUTES REQUIRED TO BRING THE UNIT FROM THE LOWEST STATE OF READINESS TO A CONDITION WHERE FLIGHT OPERATIONS MAY TAKE PLACE.

Name: TOTAL TRANSIT TIME TO AND FROM OPAREA
BOTTOM TIME IN MINUTES
Explanation: THE TIME FROM "LEFT SURFACE" TO "LEFT BOTTOM".

Name: RESPONSE TIME IN MINUTES
Explanation: TIME BEFORE A UNIT CAN RESPOND TO A MISSION REQUEST.

Name: TIME RELATIVE TO H-HOUR IN MINUTES
DURATION OF FIRE IN MINUTES RELATIVE TO H-HOUR
RESERVATION START TIME
Explanation: THE TIME, RELATIVE TO H-HOUR, AT WHICH A FIRE UNIT RESERVATION STARTS.

Name: RESERVATION STOP TIME
Explanation: THE TIME, RELATIVE TO H-HOUR, AT WHICH A FIRE UNIT RESERVATION ENDS.

Name: TIME IN MINUTES BETWEEN MARCHING GROUPS
Explanation: THE INDIVIDUAL TIME INTERVAL BETWEEN MARCHING GROUPS.

Name: TIME IN MINUTES BETWEEN CONVOYS
Explanation: THE INDIVIDUAL TIME INTERVAL BETWEEN CONVOYS.

Name: TIME IN MINUTES BETWEEN PACKETS
Explanation: THE INDIVIDUAL TIME INTERVAL BETWEEN MARCHING PACKETS.

Name: PASS TIME IN MINUTES, AUTOBAHNEN FREEWAYS
Explanation: THE PASS TIME IN MINUTES TO BE MAINTAINED BY MARCHING UNITS ON AUTOBAHNEN AND FREEWAYS.

Name: PASS TIME IN MINUTES, OTHER ROADS
Explanation: THE PASS TIME IN MINUTES TO BE MAINTAINED BY MARCHING UNITS ON ROADS OTHER THAN AUTOBAHNEN AND FREEWAYS.

Name: TIME TO PREP UNREP RIG IN MIN
Explanation: THE TIME IN MINUTES REQUIRED TO BRING THE UNIT FROM THE LOWEST STATE OF READINESS TO A CONDITION WHERE UNDERWAY REPLENISHMENT MAY TAKE PLACE.
